Record Test Commands:

Record on a specific browser: npx playwright codegen --browser chromium (firefox etc)

Emulate the device: npx playwright codegen --device="iPhone 11"

Record and save to a file: npx playwright codegen --target javascript -o record_ example.js

Set viewport, screen resolution (size): npx playwright codegen --viewport-size=800,600

Emulate color scheme: npx playwright codegen --color-scheme=dark (if available on the website)

See all options: npx playwright codegen --help



Start tests (all): npx playwright test

Start a specific test: npx playwright test tests/login.luckystake.spec.ts
